https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/book/e/29/t/heaven--is-it-for-real-

The Sony Pictures film Heaven Is for Real has been billed as an inspirational movie event for everyone, but it is specifically targeted at Christian audiences. Yet what if, lurking inside its feel-good packaging and uplifting message about heaven and eternal life, it contained a message that directly contradicts the very teachings of the Bible?
